===World (European) Under-21 Championship===
* [[1986 Individual Speedway Junior European Championship|1986]] {{flagicon|USSR}} [[Rivne]] - 4th - 10pts

===Speedway World Team Cup===
* [[1990 Speedway World Team Cup|1990]] - {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Pardubice]] - 4th - 19pts (6)
* [[1999 Speedway World Team Cup|1999]] - {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Pardubice]] - '''2nd''' - 35pts (9)

===Speedway World Cup===
* [[2002 Speedway World Cup Final|2002]] - {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Peterborough]], [[East of England Showground]] - 5th - 36pts (5)

===Speedway World Pairs Championship===
* [[1989 Speedway World Pairs Championship|1989]] - {{flagicon|POL}} [[Leszno]], [[Alfred Smoczyk Stadium]] (with [[Zdenek Tesar]]) - 7th - 25pts (14)
* [[1991 Speedway World Pairs Championship|1991]] - {{flagicon|POL}} [[Pozna<U+0144>]], [[Olimpia Pozna<U+0144> Stadium]] (with [[Roman Matousek]]) - 5th 18pts (12)

===Individual European Championship===
* [[2001 Individual Speedway European Championship|2001]] - {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Heusden-Zolder]], [[Heusden-Zolder Speedway]] - '''Winner''' - 14pts
* [[2002 Individual Speedway European Championship|2002]] - {{flagicon|POL}} [[Rybnik]], [[Rybnik Municipal Stadium]] - 5th - 10pts

===European Pairs Championship===
* [[2004 European Pairs Speedway Championship|2004]] - '''Winner''' - 28pts (16)
* [[2005 European Pairs Speedway Championship|2005]] - '''2nd''' - 27pts (13+4)
* [[2006 European Pairs Speedway Championship|2006]] - 4th - 15pts (0)

===European Club Champions' Cup===
* [[1998 European Speedway Club Champions' Cup|1998]] - '''2nd''' - 36pts (9)
* [[2004 European Speedway Club Champions' Cup|2004]] - 4th - 42pts (12)

===Individual Czechoslovakian Championship===
* 1986 - 15th - 17pts
* 1987 - 16th - 19pts
* 1988 - 6th - 53pts
* 1989 - 4th - 61pts
* 1991 - '''2nd''' - 14pts

===Individual Czech Republic Championship===
* 1992 - '''Winner''' - 15pts
* 1993 - '''Winner''' - 14pts
* 1994 - 4th - 11pts + 2pts
* 1995 - 10 - 6pts
* 1996 - '''3rd''' - 13pts + 1pt
* 1997 - '''2nd''' - 13pts + 1pts
* 1998 - '''Winner''' - 14pts
* 1999 - '''3rd''' - 12pts
* 2000 - '''Winner''' - 50pts
* 2001 - '''Winner''' - 75pts
* 2002 - '''2nd''' - 14pts + 2pts
* 2004 - '''Winner''' - 14pts + 3pts

===Individual Junior Czechoslovakian Championship===
* 1983 - 16th - 32pts
* 1985 - '''Winner''' - 43pts

